{ lib, buildRosPackage, fetchurl, ament-copyright, ament-flake8, ament-pep257, diagnostic-aggregator, diagnostic-msgs, diagnostic-updater, irobot-create-msgs, pythonPackages, rclpy, sensor-msgs }:
